# Egress allowlist (POSIX extended regex, one host pattern per line).
# Only destinations matching a line here are reachable; everything else — every
# LAN address included — is denied by `FilterDefaultDeny Yes`.
#
# Anthropic-owned domains cover the API, the login/OAuth token exchange, and
# feature-flag/telemetry (statsig.anthropic.com). Add a line if your workflow
# needs another host — keep it as tight as possible.
(^|\.)anthropic\.com$
(^|\.)claude\.ai$
(^|\.)claude\.com$
platform\.claude\.com$

# GitHub — web/API (github.com, api.github.com, codeload.github.com) and file
# content / release assets (raw.githubusercontent.com, objects.github...).
# Public hosts only; this does not grant any LAN access.
(^|\.)github\.com$
(^|\.)githubusercontent\.com$
